fulltitle: Gary Bartz Talks About Drug Use Among Jazz Greats
title: Gary Bartz Talks About Drug Use Among Jazz Greats
description: Legendary saxophonist Gary Bartz talks about drug use among jazz greats, how he got hooked, kicking the habit and the effects on the music.
